      <scopecontent id="aspace_87f248fb17708019c762127e080234e2">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The materials consists of unbound photograph albums of Philip Hinkle (Yale 1897) documenting his student days at Yale. Includes photographs of Glee Club trips, sports, group and individual portraits of classmates, campus scenes, and pictures of family, friends, and trips.</p>  
